headline.main: AFFAIRS IN FRANCE.; The Effect of the Peace Negotiations. THE LATE DUELS. THE CENT-GARDES. The Actresses' Ball, &c.

docs.lead_paragraph: THINGS AT THE PALACE. A-week ultra-pacific-a week of rise at the Bourse, and of rise in public spirits. LOUIS NAPOLEON has pronounced the words, "If Russia makes one step towards peace, I will make two," and Paris is gay, for it believes in peace.
